* âœ¨ Add examples for AuthX authentication. PR [#738](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/738) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).
* ğŸ—ï¸ Update CI workflow to use only Ubuntu. PR [#736](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/736) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).
