## 1.4.0

__Note:__ This release contains breaking changes, Dropping support for Python 3.8, and adding support for Python 3.13.

### Breaking Changes

* ğŸ”§ Add support for Python 3.13. PR [#687](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/687) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).

### Fixes

* ğŸ› fix Missing `Audience` & `Issuer` in the verify token. PR [#686](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/686) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).

### Upgrades

* â¬†ï¸ï¸ Bump starlette from 0.39.2 to 0.40.0. PR [#688](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/688) by [@dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot).
* â¬†ï¸ï¸ Bump the python-packages group with 16 updates. PR [#685](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/685) by [@dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot).
* â¬†ï¸ï¸ Bump the Pre-commit Dependencies Version. PR [#684](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/684) by [@pre-commit-ci[bot]](https://github.com/apps/pre-commit-ci).
* â¬†ï¸ï¸ Bump pypa/gh-action-pypi-publish from 1.10.2 to 1.10.3. PR [#681](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/681) by [@dependabot[bot]](https://github.com/apps/dependabot).
* â¬†ï¸ï¸ï¸ Update dependencies in `uv.lock`. PR [#680](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/680) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).
* â¬†ï¸ï¸ Bump `ruff-pre-commit` from v0.6.7 to v0.6.8. PR [#678](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/678) by [@pre-commit-ci[bot]](https://github.com/apps/pre-commit-ci).

