* â™»ï¸ Refactor Installation of `authx_extra` package. PR [#575](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/575) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).
* ğŸ“ Add extra API documentation files. PR [#569](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/569) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).

