## 1.0.0

### Core

* âœ¨ authx Revamp - V1.0.0. PR [#446](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/446) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123)
* â™»ï¸ Refactor & Rebuild Functionalities in authx. PR [#454](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/454) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123)
* âœ¨ Migrate Authx to use pydantic v2. PR [#531](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/531) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123)
* âœ¨ Handle catch-all signature errors. PR [#538](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/538) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123)
* â™»ï¸ Drop External Libraries in favour of `authx-extra`. PR [#506](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/506) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123)

