## 1.0.1b1

!!! warning
    This is a beta release. Please do not use in production.

### Documentations

* ğŸ“ Add Basic Documentation for authx core. PR [#513](https://github.com/yezz123/authx/pull/513) by [@yezz123](https://github.com/yezz123).
